{{! Hackathon template – same 8 sections with hackathon-specific framing }}
<!-- ===== 1. EXECUTIVE SUMMARY ===== -->
<div class="section avoid-break">
    <div class="section-header">
        <div class="section-number">1</div>
        <div class="section-title">Executive <span class="accent">Summary</span></div>
    </div>
    <p>{{executiveSummary}}</p>
</div>

<!-- ===== 2. INSTITUTIONAL OVERVIEW ===== -->
<div class="section avoid-break">
    <div class="section-header">
        <div class="section-number">2</div>
        <div class="section-title">Institutional <span class="accent">Overview</span></div>
    </div>
    <div class="info-grid">
        <div class="info-card">
            <label>Institution Name</label>
            <span>{{institution.name}}</span>
        </div>
        <div class="info-card">
            <label>Institution Type</label>
            <span>{{titleCase institution.type}}</span>
        </div>
        <div class="info-card">
            <label>Location</label>
            <span>{{institution.location}}</span>
        </div>
        {{#if institution.established}}
        <div class="info-card">
            <label>Year Established</label>
            <span>{{institution.established}}</span>
        </div>
        {{/if}}
        {{#if institution.studentCount}}
        <div class="info-card">
            <label>Student Enrolment</label>
            <span>{{institution.studentCount}} students</span>
        </div>
        {{/if}}
        {{#if institution.accreditation}}
        <div class="info-card">
            <label>Accreditation</label>
            <span>{{institution.accreditation}}</span>
        </div>
        {{/if}}
        <div class="info-card full-width">
            <label>Academic Departments</label>
            <span>{{join institution.departments ', '}}</span>
        </div>
        {{#if institution.vision}}
        <div class="info-card full-width">
            <label>Institutional Vision</label>
            <span>{{institution.vision}}</span>
        </div>
        {{/if}}
    </div>
</div>

<!-- ===== 3. IDENTIFIED GAPS ===== -->
<div class="section page-break">
    <div class="section-header">
        <div class="section-number">3</div>
        <div class="section-title">Identified <span class="accent">Gaps</span></div>
    </div>
    <p>The identified gaps below are systematically scored using a multi-factor prioritization algorithm and serve as
        the thematic basis for defining hackathon problem tracks. Each gap will be translated into one or more
        structured problem statements to drive focused innovation during the event.</p>

    {{#if criticalGaps.length}}
    <div
        style="background:#fef2f2; border-left:4px solid #dc2626; border-radius:0 8px 8px 0; padding:12px 20px; margin-bottom:20px;">
        <strong style="color:#dc2626;">⚠ Critical Priority Alert:</strong>
        <span style="color:#374151;"> {{criticalGaps.length}} gap(s) classified as Critical will serve as mandatory
            hackathon problem tracks requiring solution prototypes within the event duration.</span>
    </div>
    {{/if}}

    <table class="gap-table">
        <thead>
            <tr>
                <th>Rank</th>
                <th>Gap Title</th>
                <th>Category</th>
                <th>Severity</th>
                <th>Score</th>
                <th>Affected Departments</th>
            </tr>
        </thead>
        <tbody>
            {{#each rankedGaps}}
            <tr>
                <td><span class="rank-badge">{{this.rank}}</span></td>
                <td style="font-weight:600; color:#0f3460; max-width:180px;">{{this.title}}</td>
                <td><span style="font-size:9pt; color:#6366f1;">{{titleCase this.category}}</span></td>
                <td><span class="badge {{severityClass this.severity}}">{{this.severity}}</span></td>
                <td>
                    <div class="score-bar-wrapper">
                        <div class="score-bar">
                            <div class="score-bar-fill" style="width:{{this.score}}0%"></div>
                        </div>
                        <span class="score-text">{{this.score}}/10</span>
                    </div>
                </td>
                <td style="font-size:9pt; color:#374151;">{{join this.affectedDepartments ', '}}</td>
            </tr>
            {{/each}}
        </tbody>
    </table>
</div>

<!-- ===== 4. PRIMARY OBJECTIVES ===== -->
<div class="section avoid-break">
    <div class="section-header">
        <div class="section-number">4</div>
        <div class="section-title">Primary <span class="accent">Objectives</span></div>
    </div>
    <ol class="objectives-list">
        {{#each objectives}}
        <li>{{this}}</li>
        {{/each}}
    </ol>
</div>

<!-- ===== 5. PROPOSED SOLUTION ===== -->
<div class="section page-break">
    <div class="section-header">
        <div class="section-number">5</div>
        <div class="section-title">Proposed <span class="accent">Hackathon Framework</span></div>
    </div>
    <p>{{proposedSolution.overview}}</p>

    <p style="font-weight:700; color:#0f3460; margin-bottom:8px;">Event Core Components</p>
    <ul class="styled-list">
        {{#each proposedSolution.components}}
        <li>{{this}}</li>
        {{/each}}
    </ul>

    <p style="font-weight:700; color:#0f3460; margin-bottom:12px; margin-top:16px;">Gap-Specific Problem Track
        Definitions</p>
    {{#each proposedSolution.gapSpecificApproaches}}
    <div
        style="background:#f8faff; border:1px solid #e0e7ff; border-radius:8px; padding:14px 18px; margin-bottom:12px;">
        <div style="display:flex; justify-content:space-between; align-items:center; margin-bottom:6px;">
            <span style="font-weight:700; color:#0f3460; font-size:10.5pt;">Track: {{this.gap}}</span>
            <span style="font-size:8pt; color:#6366f1; font-weight:600;">Rank #{{this.rank}} · Priority Score:
                {{this.score}}/10</span>
        </div>
        <p style="font-size:10pt; color:#374151; margin:0;">{{this.approach}}</p>
    </div>
    {{/each}}
</div>

<!-- ===== 6. IMPLEMENTATION PLAN ===== -->
<div class="section page-break">
    <div class="section-header">
        <div class="section-number">6</div>
        <div class="section-title">Implementation <span class="accent">Plan</span></div>
    </div>
    <div class="timeline-summary-bar">
        <div class="timeline-summary-card">
            <label>Total Duration</label>
            <span>{{timeline.totalDuration}}</span>
        </div>
        <div class="timeline-summary-card">
            <label>Proposed Start</label>
            <span>{{timeline.proposedStartDate}}</span>
        </div>
        <div class="timeline-summary-card">
            <label>Proposed End</label>
            <span>{{timeline.proposedEndDate}}</span>
        </div>
    </div>
    <p style="font-size:9.5pt; color:#6b7280; font-style:italic; margin-bottom:20px;">{{timeline.complexityNote}}</p>
    {{#each timeline.phases}}
    <div class="phase-card avoid-break">
        <div class="phase-header">
            <span class="phase-name">{{this.phase}}: {{this.name}}</span>
            <span class="phase-meta">{{this.duration}} &nbsp;|&nbsp; {{this.weekRange}}</span>
        </div>
        <ul class="phase-activities">
            {{#each this.activities}}
            <li>{{this}}</li>
            {{/each}}
        </ul>
    </div>
    {{/each}}
</div>

<!-- ===== 7. EXPECTED OUTCOMES ===== -->
<div class="section page-break">
    <div class="section-header">
        <div class="section-number">7</div>
        <div class="section-title">Expected <span class="accent">Outcomes</span></div>
    </div>
    <p style="font-weight:700; color:#0f3460; margin-bottom:8px;">Immediate Event Outcomes</p>
    <ul class="styled-list">
        {{#each expectedOutcomes.shortTermOutcomes}}
        <li>{{this}}</li>
        {{/each}}
    </ul>
    <p style="font-weight:700; color:#0f3460; margin-bottom:8px; margin-top:16px;">Long-Term Innovation Impact</p>
    <ul class="styled-list">
        {{#each expectedOutcomes.longTermOutcomes}}
        <li>{{this}}</li>
        {{/each}}
    </ul>
    <p style="font-weight:700; color:#0f3460; margin-bottom:12px; margin-top:20px;">Key Performance Indicators (KPIs)
    </p>
    <table class="kpi-table">
        <thead>
            <tr>
                <th>Performance Indicator</th>
                <th>Target</th>
                <th>Measurement Methodology</th>
            </tr>
        </thead>
        <tbody>
            {{#each expectedOutcomes.kpis}}
            <tr>
                <td style="font-weight:600; color:#0f3460;">{{this.indicator}}</td>
                <td>{{this.target}}</td>
                <td>{{this.measurement}}</td>
            </tr>
            {{/each}}
        </tbody>
    </table>
</div>

<!-- ===== 8. BUDGET ESTIMATE ===== -->
<div class="section avoid-break">
    <div class="section-header">
        <div class="section-number">8</div>
        <div class="section-title">Budget <span class="accent">Estimate</span></div>
    </div>
    <p>The hackathon budget encompasses venue and logistics, prize distribution, promotional activities, technology
        infrastructure, and expert mentorship honoraria. The following estimate reflects a preliminary projection and is
        subject to sponsor contributions and institutional co-funding arrangements.</p>
    <table class="budget-table">
        <tbody>
            <tr>
                <td><strong>Setup &amp; Administration</strong></td>
                <td style="text-align:right; font-weight:600;">{{budget.breakdown.setupAndAdministration}}</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <td><strong>Gap-Track Problem Development Costs</strong></td>
                <td style="text-align:right; font-weight:600;">{{budget.breakdown.gapAddressingCosts}}</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <td><strong>Prize Pool &amp; Logistics</strong></td>
                <td style="text-align:right; font-weight:600;">{{budget.breakdown.programSpecificCosts}}</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <td><strong>Contingency Reserve</strong></td>
                <td style="text-align:right; font-weight:600;">{{budget.breakdown.contingencyReserve}}</td>
            </tr>
            <tr class="total-row">
                <td>ESTIMATED TOTAL (USD)</td>
                <td style="text-align:right;">{{budget.estimatedTotalUSD}}</td>
            </tr>
            <tr class="total-row" style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1a1a2e, #0f3460);">
                <td>ESTIMATED TOTAL (INR)</td>
                <td style="text-align:right;">{{budget.estimatedTotalINR}}</td>
            </tr>
        </tbody>
    </table>
    <div class="budget-note">{{budget.note}}</div>
</div>